# Caddy reverse proxy → clean HTTPS in front of the M7.1 app.
# Caddy auto-provisions + renews a free Let's Encrypt cert for this hostname
# (TLS-ALPN-01 on :443), so the app is reachable at https://m71long.duckdns.org
# with no port and a valid padlock. `m71` is the compose service name; Caddy
# reaches the app over the shared compose network at m71:5050.
m71long.duckdns.org {
	reverse_proxy m71:5050
}
